    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a pristine example of the E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power unit. This high-revving naturally aspirated mill utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox, the drivetrain is complemented by a factory-spec limited-slip differential. This chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a preventative VANOS overhaul to ensure structural and mechanical longevity. The suspension geometry remains taut, with all bushings and dampers in peak operational state. Finished in a concours-grade exterior with a flawless interior, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the discerning collector seeking peak BMW M-division engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
