      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a true time capsule for the discerning collector. The exterior retains its deep, mirror-like factory finish, protected by a professional ceramic coating with absolutely no rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in an 'as-new' state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is flawless, having been meticulously maintained at scheduled intervals with a full paper trail of service records included. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting its life in a climate-controlled garage. This is an investment-grade example that drives as perfectly as it looks, offering a rare opportunity to own a piece of automotive excellence in its purest form.",
      "price": 48500.0,
